---
import { Picture } from 'astro:assets'
import webappImage from '../assets/webapp.jpg'
import marketingsiteImage from '../assets/marketingsite.jpg'
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout title='CRU - Custom Software'>
  <div class='space-y-12'>
    <h1>Custom Software</h1>
    <p>
      Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nullam dolor purus,
      ullamcorper a mauris vitae, auctor dictum nisl. Duis auctor, metus vel rutrum
      iaculis, sapien dolor placerat nisi, at blandit massa leo quis enim. Praesent in
      ornare elit, vel ornare neque. Nulla bibendum, eros non molestie tincidunt, odio
      augue condimentum dolor, rhoncus finibus orci nisl ut tellus.
    </p>

    <div class='mx-auto grid grid-cols-2 gap-16 pt-32'>
      <div
        class='relative isolate overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-gray-900 px-8 pb-8 pt-80 sm:pt-48 lg:pt-80'
      >
        <Picture
          src={webappImage}
          formats={['avif', 'webp']}
          height={800}
          alt='web-apps'
          class='absolute inset-0 -z-10 h-full w-full object-cover'
        />
        <div
          class='absolute inset-0 -z-10 bg-gradient-to-t from-gray-900 via-gray-900/20'
        >
        </div>
        <div
          class='absolute inset-0 -z-10 rounded-2xl ring-1 ring-inset ring-gray-900/10'
        >
        </div>

        <div
          class='flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-1 overflow-hidden text-sm leading-6 text-brand-primary-400'
        >
          <div class='flex items-center gap-x-4'>
            <div class='flex gap-x-2.5'>Powerful web applications for any need</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h2 class='text-white'>
          <a href='/custom-software/webapps'>
            <span class='absolute inset-0'></span>
             Web apps
          </a>
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div
        class='relative isolate overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-gray-900 px-8 pb-8 pt-80 sm:pt-48 lg:pt-80'
      >
        <Picture
          src={marketingsiteImage}
          formats={['avif', 'webp']}
          height={800}
          alt='web-apps'
          class='absolute inset-0 -z-10 h-full w-full object-cover'
        />
        <div
          class='absolute inset-0 -z-10 bg-gradient-to-t from-gray-900 via-gray-900/40'
        >
        </div>
        <div
          class='absolute inset-0 -z-10 rounded-2xl ring-1 ring-inset ring-gray-900/10'
        >
        </div>

        <div
          class='flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-1 overflow-hidden text-sm leading-6 text-brand-primary-400'
        >
          <div class='flex items-center gap-x-4'>
            <div class='flex gap-x-2.5'>Simple websites for brand awareness</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h2 class='text-white'>
          <a href='/product/1'>
            <span class='absolute inset-0'></span>
             Marketing sites
          </a>
        </h2>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
